				<Content>When AGENT reached out to us to write an introduction to his book, we couldnâ€™t say yes faster. AGENT may not have been the first agent we talked to, but he was certainly the last. </Content>
			</CharacterStyleRange>
			<CharacterStyleRange AppliedCharacterStyle="CharacterStyle/$ID/[No character style]" CharacterDirection="RightToLeftDirection">
